high_descs: Turn left, proceed to stove, turn left, proceed to end of counter.  Turn left and left again to face counter.
Pick up knife from counter in front of plate.
Turn left, then right, proceed around counter to stove.
Place knife in pot on right lower burner.
Pick up pan with knife in it.
Turn around, proceed to counter.  Turn left to face counter.
Put pan with knife on right edge of counter, to right and behind apple, on top of spatula.
anns.task_desc: Put knife in pot, put knife and pot on counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the oven, then hang a left and walk to the far side of the kitchen island.
Pick up the butter knife off of the kitchen island.
Turn left and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the stove.
Put the butter knife in the deep metal pan that is on the front right burner of the stove.
Pick up the metal pan with the butter knife in it.
Turn around and walk towards the counter, then turn left and walk up to the kitchen island.
Put the pan with the butter knife in it on the kitchen island to the right of the apple.
anns.task_desc: Put a deep pan with a butter knife in it on the kitchen island.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the other side of the island, face the knife on the island.
Pick up the knife that's in front of the brown plate.
Turn left and walk to the stove on the left.
Place the knife inside of the pan to the right of the kettle.
Pick up the pan with the knife in it.
Turn around and walk to the island in the middle of the kitchen and face the apple and head of lettuce.
Put the pan down on the island to the right of the apple.
anns.task_desc: To move a pan and knife to the kitchen island.
